= Sitemap Search

Originally created by Sean Cribbs, fall 2007.  Revised and generalized August
2008.

Provides a simple search for pages within the sitemap.  Contains rudimentary
support for scoping searches within a given site when using the multi_site
extension.

= Acknowledgments

Thanks to Digital Pulp for funding the initial development of this extension
as part of the Redken.com project.

Further support for generalization and release was provided by Con-way.